com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class ProcessProductionOrdersService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.ProcessProductionOrdersService

  • public class ProcessProductionOrdersService
extends Object

    You can use this service to read header data, items, operations, components, and the status of production order. With this API, it is also possible to release a production order or an operation of a production order.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_PRODUCTION_ORDERS
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1702
    Communication Scenario:Production Planning Integration (SAP_COM_0104)
    Scope Items:Material Requirements Planning (J44)
